cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.MM

This paper focuses on gesture-based human-robot interaction, which involves computer vision and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The application of the pipeline is in robotics, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics and Control). The paper also discusses the practicality of the method for robot applications, which falls under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper mentions the use of a dataset, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia).
